---
title: Warm Vegan Arugula & Grain Bowls with Grape Tomatoes, Cashews & Sherry Vinaigrette
description: This vibrant vegan grain bowl layers nutty grains with peppery arugula, juicy grape tomatoes, crisp cucumber, and scallions. It’s topped with crunchy cashews and a bold sherry vinegar–red pepper vinaigrette for a warm, satisfying dish that’s fresh, flavorful, and full of texture in every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HFUSRC_R61498A_Hero_WarmVeganArugulaAndGrainBowls_W50_9_2025_Web-f2020d23.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65c26d14606e44bed253844c-en-US.pdf
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 530 kcal
  fat: 25 g
  saturated fat: 4 g
  carbohydrates: 64 g
  sugar: 14 g
  protein: 9 g
  fiber: 5 g
  sodium: 350 mg
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/vegan-warm-greens-and-grains-bowls-65c26d14606e44bed253844c
time required: 15m
---

Wash and dry produce.

Trim and thinly slice @scallions{2}. Trim and quarter @mini cucumber{1} lengthwise; thinly
slice into quarter-moons. Halve @grape tomatoes{4%oz}.

In a large #bowl{}, whisk together @sherry vinegar{5%tsp}, @Dijon mustard{4%tsp},
@red pepper jam{1}, @olive oil{2%tbsp}, @salt{tsp}, and @black pepper{tsp} until combined.
To bowl with dressing, add scallions, cucumber, and tomatoes; toss until evenly coated.

Massage @microwavable grain blend{1} in package; partially open top. Microwave until
warmed through, ~{1.5-2%minutes}. Transfer to bowl with veggies and toss until evenly
coated.

Add @arugula{2%oz} and @cashews{1%oz}; toss until well combined. Taste and season with
salt and pepper if desired.

Divide salad between bowls and serve.